1) CIS 162 Social Media Course – 3 credits

Course Description: Learn about and practice with commonly-used social media channels, including Facebook, LinkedIn, and Twitter. Develop a content media strategy and produce meaningful content for business cases.

Outcomes:
•	List five major social media channels businesses use
•	Explain how social media helps businesses 
•	Compare and contrast social media and content marketing
•	Describe conversion rate optimization (CRO)
•	Develop a content media strategy that includes analytics
